{"tid":126250,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[東方joke球] 經東方買作客恆大飛既球迷一律冇飛 每位賠償$3000","createTime":"2017-02-19T08:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T19:10:49.000Z","uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb281e97cad15c769c185380236c41dce87d2a4d","tid":126250,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:06:46.000Z","msg":"【東方亞冠球迷打氣活動酒店現場】<br />\n早前經東方龍獅官方買咗客對恆大嘅球迷收到通知，今日晏晝嚟逸東酒店出席球迷活動，話有重要事項宣佈。<br />\n東方龍獅總監梁守志喺會場表示，因為出咗一啲問題，所有經東方買作客門票嘅球迷都無飛，球迷未能隨隊北上，至於發生咩事，將會喺聽日公佈。對於今次事件，將會退款同賠償畀買咗飛嘅球迷每位$3,000。<br />\n為咗畀球迷有另一渠道支持球隊，東方將會喺2月22日夜晚7點鐘喺灣仔RedMR舉行睇波打氣派對。"},{"pid":"a65ea45f70cf5fa29077b89f21b3cb46032648d7","tid":126250,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:14:08.000Z","msg":"屌你狗志啲飛去哂邊"},{"pid":"812a1c456a1447fbd3e2ca6f0bb515f765fa2305","tid":126250,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:16:23.000Z","msg":"狗志食撚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f1469c447e85cfbde47834faff7d8dc8e41f87","tid":126250,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗志食撚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c8d0d9cdb348ce0cefa8e1d36a2b2a92255623","tid":126250,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:59:16.000Z","msg":"狗志同雲加仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed36837fd4fd26e45651492a3bae1e014951d33","tid":126250,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>狗志食撚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></b